Package: tdcsStatistics
Type: Project
Title: tDCS Anatomy Montage Optimization - Statistical Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Statistical analysis pipeline for transcranial direct current 
    stimulation (tDCS) anatomy-based montage optimization. Includes generalized
    linear mixed-effects models (GLM), functional network analysis, principal
    component analysis (PCA), and specialized morphological analyses. Supports
    per-subject, per-parcel, and population-level analyses across multiple
    electrode montages and simulation conditions.
